### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/health

### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "organizador@randomfates.test",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "organizador@randomfates.test",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Crear sorteo
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/raffles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sorteo lanzamiento RandomFates",
  "description": "Demo de ruleta verificable",
  "type": "ROULETTE",
  "configuration": {
    "winnersCount": 1,
    "animation": "roulette"
  },
  "isPublic": true
}

### Crear premio
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/raffles/{{raffleId}}/prizes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gift card",
  "description": "Premio principal",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Carga masiva de participantes
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/raffles/{{raffleId}}/participants/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "participantes-demo.json",
  "participants": [
    { "fullName": "Ana Torres", "identifier": "DNI-001", "email": "ana@test.com" },
    { "fullName": "Luis Rojas", "identifier": "DNI-002", "email": "luis@test.com" }
  ]
}

### Publicar
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/raffles/{{raffleId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Ejecutar
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/raffles/{{raffleId}}/executions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}
